---
title: Peking-Style Tofu & Snow Pea Salad with Roasted Kumara & Soy Mayo
description: Enjoy a fresh fusion of Asian-style flavours with this hearty, pretty-as-a-picture salad. Chunks of roasted kumara tossed with snow peas, Peking tofu and other tasty delights will have you savouring every bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5e4df4aabbca4f4bc62a9520-1ac6d474.jpg
